==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Saltimbanco
<hw>Sal`tim*ban"co</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[It.,
literally, one who leaps or mounts upon a bench; <ets>saltare</ets> to
leap + <ets>in</ets> in, upon + <ets>banco</ets> a bench.]</ety> <def>A
mountebank; a quack.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>santinbanco</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Saltimbancos</qex>, quacksalvers, and charlatans.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir T. Browne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>saltiness</ent>⟦br⟧
